code: @Override public boolean equals(Object obj) {     Match o = (Match) obj.     if (left == null && o.left == null && right.equals(o.right)) {         return true.     } else if (right == null && o.right == null && left.equals(o.left)) {         return true.     } else {         return this.left.equals(o.left) && this.right.equals(o.right).     } }

@Override public int hashCode() {     if (left == null) {         return right.hashCode().     } else if (right == null) {         return left.hashCode().     } else {         return this.left.hashCode() ^ this.right.hashCode().     } }
@Override public String toString() {     return left + ", " + right. }
